				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Do NOT walk away from the nexus bankers with bags open, this can cause you to crash to server select (I had done this several times).
<br />

<br />
The irritating thing is, the last time I did it I lost an item in bag #3:
<br />

<br />
xx
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">X</span>x
<br />
xx
<br />
xx
<br />

<br />
Slot #4
<br />

<br />
xx
<br />
x<span style="font-weight: bold">X</span>
<br />
xx
<br />
xx
<br />

<br />
makes me wonder how many more items I might have lost unknowingly.
<br />

<br />
Just an FYI, since SoE doesn't relate "reported" bugs to the communities, and I'd hate to see anyone lose anything of value (thankfully for me it was only an item worth 400pp).</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
