When I logged in after a visit to the bank in <span style="font-style: italic">Bazaar</span>, I found that my favorite <span style="font-style: italic">Enshrouded Veil</span> had disappeared from my person.  I <span style="text-decoration: underline">never</span> take it off or switch it out for another mask, so I could not have dropped it.
